vies of 2019|first=Matt|last=Singer|website=ScreenCrush}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} David Crow \u2013 [[Den of Geek]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.denofgeek.com/us/go/282640|title=10 Best Movies of 2019|website=Den of Geek}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} [[Film Comment]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.filmcomment.com/best-films-of-2019/|title=Best Films of 2019|website=Film Comment}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} [[Film School Rejects]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://filmschoolrejects.com/best-movies-2019/|title=The 50 Best Movies of 2019|date=December 31, 2019|website=Film School Rejects}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Katie Rife \u2013 ''The A.V. Club''<ref name=\"auto3\"/>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Roxana Hadadi \u2013 ''The A.V. Club''<ref name=\"auto3\"/>\n* 3rd{{snd}} [[Stephanie Zacharek]] \u2013 ''[[Time (magazine)|Time]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://time.com/5737103/best-movies-2019/|title=The 10 Best Movies of 2019|website=Time}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Clayton Dillard \u2013 ''Slant''<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Michael Barker \u2013 [[Film at Lincoln Center]]<ref name=\"auto2\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/best-movies-2019-indie-film-community-1202198566/|title=The Best Films of 2019, According to the Independent Film Community|first1=Eric|last1=Kohn|first2=Eric|last2=Kohn|date=December 24, 2019}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Wes Greene \u2013 ''Slant''<ref name=\"auto5\"/>\n* 3rd{{snd}} Bob Strauss \u2013 ''[[Los Angeles Daily News]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.dailynews.com/2019-was-a-terrific-year-for-movies-here-are-12-films-you-have-to-see|title=2019 was a terrific year for movies. Here are 12 films you have to see|date=December 17, 2019}}</ref>\n* 3rd{{snd}} [[Online Film Critics Society]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ofcs.org/ofcs-presents-22nd-annual-nominations-for-2018-2-2/|title=OFCS Presents: 23rd Annual Awards for 2019|first=Governing|last=Committee|date=January 7, 2020}}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} [[Kyle Smith]] \u2013 ''[[National Review]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.nationalreview.com/2019/12/movie-review-ten-best-films-2019/|title=The Ten Best Films of 2019|date=December 23, 2019}}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} Tomris Laffly \u2013 RogerEbert.com<ref name=\"auto4\"/>\n* 4th{{snd}} IndieWire (300+ Critics Survey)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiewire.com/2019/12/best-movies-2019-critics-survey-poll-performances-parasite-adam-driver-lupita-nyongo-1202197615/|title=2019 Critics Poll: The Best Films and Performances According to Over 300 Critics From Around the World|first1=Eric|last1=Kohn|first2=Eric|last2=Kohn|date=December 16, 2019}}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} Ignatiy Vishnevetsky \u2013 ''The A.V. Club''<ref name=\"auto3\"/>\n* 4th{{snd}} David Sims \u2013 ''[[The Atlantic]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2019/12/10-best-films-2019/602797/|title=The 10 Best Films of 2019|first=David|last=Sims|date=December 5, 2019|website=The Atlantic}}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} Vinnie Mancuso \u2013 [[Collider (website)|Collider]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://collider.com/best-movies-of-the-year-2019/|title=Vinnie Mancuso's Top 10 Films of 2019|first=Vinnie|last=Mancuso|date=December 10, 2019}}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} [[Sight & Sound]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://theplaylist.net/souvenir-parasite-sight-sounds-top-20-films-2019-20191201/|title='The Souvenir,' 'Parasite' Top Sight & Sound's Top 20 Films Of 2019|website=theplaylist.net}}</ref>\n* 4th{{snd}} ''[[Complex (magazine)|Complex]]''<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.complex.com/pop-culture/best-movies-of-2019/|title=The Best Movies of 2019'Once Upon a Time... in Hollywood'|website=Complex}}</ref>\n* 5th{{snd}} Alissa Wilkinson \u2013 [[Vox (website)|Vox]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vox.com/2019/12/5/20983881/best-movies-2019-streaming-how-to-watch|title=The 21 best films of 2019|first=Alissa|last=Wilkinson|date=December 5, 2019|website=Vox}}</ref>\n* 5th{{snd}} Kate Erbland \u2013 IndieWire<ref name=\"auto1\"/>\n* 5th{{snd}} Christopher Gray \u2013 ''Slant''<ref name=\"auto5\"/>